@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gindss(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v2 - 0.17)
    v1 = wp.exp(tmp)
    v2 = wp.cos(v0)
    v2 = wp.sin((0.56 - v2))
    v0 = (tmp / v1)
    v2 = wp.sin(0.24)
    tmp = wp.exp((0.27 + (v2 + 0.82 + tmp + 0.17)))
    v2 = 0.21
    data[tid] = v0
